snippet.title: Vapor World : Over The Mind - E3 Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Page is now available!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1996090/

Discord Channel
https://discord.gg/uBzxgTmFSU

Filled with beautiful illustrations, this special inner world is fraught with danger.
Overcome challenging battles and explore the vast inner world to uncover hidden secrets and difficulties.
 
The strange vista reflected in his eyes... Is it a dream or a reality? 
To escape the twisted world, the boy begins his journey.
